## Non-Negotiables

- [e.g., Never mock the database in integration tests]
- [e.g., All API endpoints must have request validation]
- [e.g., Use absolute imports]

## Architecture

- [e.g., Handler → Service → Store pattern for all endpoints]
- [e.g., Domain errors in pkg/errors, not raw HTTP codes]

